Today I continued my first project. 
I learnt how to:

- extend the body to full page
body {
    min-height: 100vh;
}

- setting a class to half page
.header {
    height: 50vh;
}

- adjust margins 
margin-top
margin-left
margin-right
margin-bottom
margin-block-start
margin-block-end

- darken a background image by using:
linear-gradient (rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5))
REMEMBER: red, green, blue, alpha parameter (opacity/transparency)!

- importing a font from Google
<style>
@import url (http://...)
</style>
